title: ERROR while running voxelmorph tutorial using TF 1.14 (as mentioned) in linux
body:
**Task** (what are you trying to do/register?)

2D images

**What have you tried**

Used the tutorial using tf 1.14 (as mentioned)
**Details of experiments**

Error while running the exact code as provided in the tutorial in linux (even the data used is the same)
